<section class="vcsc-reviews" id="reviews">
  <div class="vcsc-container">
    <div class="vcsc-section-header">
      <p class="vcsc-section-eyebrow">Social Proof</p>
      <h2 class="vcsc-section-title">What Our Enterprise Clients Are Saying</h2>
      <p class="vcsc-section-sub">312 verified purchasers. 312 people who did not read the code. Zero regrets on record.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="vcsc-reviews__track-wrap">
      <div class="vcsc-reviews__track" id="reviews-track">

        <div class="vcsc-review-card">
          <div class="vcsc-review-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote class="vcsc-review-card__quote">
            "Deployed 47 microservices last Tuesday. Read zero lines of code. No regrets."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="vcsc-review-card__author">
            <div class="vcsc-review-card__avatar">CW</div>
            <div class="vcsc-review-card__meta">
              <strong>Chad W.</strong>
              <span>Principal Engineer @ NullPointerAI</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vcsc-review-card">
          <div class="vcsc-review-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote class="vcsc-review-card__quote">
            "Our entire CI/CD pipeline is now just this button and a prayer. Pipeline health is up 12%. We don't know why."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="vcsc-review-card__author">
            <div class="vcsc-review-card__avatar">BK</div>
            <div class="vcsc-review-card__meta">
              <strong>Brittany K.</strong>
              <span>VP of Vibes @ ShipItNow.io</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vcsc-review-card">
          <div class="vcsc-review-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote class="vcsc-review-card__quote">
            "OSHA came. We showed them the warranty card. They left. We consider this a successful audit."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="vcsc-review-card__author">
            <div class="vcsc-review-card__avatar">DM</div>
            <div class="vcsc-review-card__meta">
              <strong>Derek M.</strong>
              <span>CTO @ AgentStack Technologies</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vcsc-review-card">
          <div class="vcsc-review-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote class="vcsc-review-card__quote">
            "I bought three. One for home, one for work, one for my therapist's desk. She said it's the most honest thing a patient has ever given her."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="vcsc-review-card__author">
            <div class="vcsc-review-card__avatar">??</div>
            <div class="vcsc-review-card__meta">
              <strong>Anonymous</strong>
              <span>Senior Developer</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vcsc-review-card">
          <div class="vcsc-review-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote class="vcsc-review-card__quote">
            "Used to spend 45 minutes reviewing AI output. Now I spend 0. My throughput is through the roof. My on-call rotation is also through the roof but that feels like a separate conversation."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="vcsc-review-card__author">
            <div class="vcsc-review-card__avatar">PR</div>
            <div class="vcsc-review-card__meta">
              <strong>Priya R.</strong>
              <span>Staff Engineer @ ContextWindowAI</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="vcsc-reviews__controls">
      <button class="vcsc-reviews__btn" id="reviews-prev" aria-label="Previous reviews">←</button>
      <div class="vcsc-reviews__dots" id="reviews-dots"></div>
      <button class="vcsc-reviews__btn" id="reviews-next" aria-label="Next reviews">→</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Fake Reviews",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
